<div id="tip"><h1><a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="start()"">×</a>测试测试测试。</h1><p><a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="showwin()">测试</a></p></div>
<div align="center"><a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="start()">点击这里测试</a>
</p>

</div>
</body>
</html>
